e perturbative 2-Star Formation Mode model, where any MS galaxy can\nexperience a continuum of different SFR enhancements. This points to a\nstarburst-merger connection not only for extreme events, but also more moderate\nbursts which merely scatter galaxies upward within the MS, rather than fully\nelevating them above it.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Sep 2018 20:42:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 16 Jun 2019 20:32:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-18"}
