^{-3}$ and\n$10^{-4}$ $yr^{-1}$. Considering the $\\delta$ Scuti nature, it may be\nspeculated that these changes are non-evolutionary.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 4 Sep 2018 10:40:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-05"}
